Name: Collapsed Link
Desc: <color=#B35353>Core algorithm module overload detected... Improve the support channel efficiency before rerunning the data simulation.</color>

Name: Here
Desc: Stranded on a shore of despair, you pass on the fragile hope to the next cycle before losing consciousness.

Name: Beyond
Desc: You gaze at the distant lights beyond, hoping to arrive there the next time.

Name: Simulation Calculation Completed
Desc: Once the environmental compatibility verification is completed, you will officially leave the ivory tower and face the malice of reality.

Name: Jetavie
Desc: <color=#B35353>The light that parts the sea of emptiness will reach another shore. Listen carefully, echo.</color>

Name: Rabbit Hole
Desc: Sweet fruits do not lead to the real Eden. Hope is a fantasy that leeches on to reality.

Name: Night Watcher
Desc: She patrols at night before dawn and indulges herself in the carefree wonderland.

Name: Daybreaker
Desc: <color=#B35353>Through the night and the shadow, a new world will be born, and the song of tomorrow will be played.</color>
